 You pick up the mailbox and open it. Inside is a single letter addressed to you. You read it. It is from your uncle, who lives in the house. He tells you that he has been ill and that you should come to his house for a visit. He says that he has a surprise for you. You put the letter back in the mailbox and close it. You walk to the house. You open the door and enter. You are in a large room with two doors
